This Erlang Program converts a DXF (binary or ASCII) to an HTML file. View it in an HTML5-ready browser (Safari, Cromium etc).

The DXF file can be created in QCAD, AUTOCAD and other CAD systems.

The parameters to dxf2js.sh is a dxffilename without extension and a layername

The dxffile should be stored in a dir ../DXF

The HTML file is created in ../DXF 

 If you want the files elswhere - change the dxf2js.sh
 
 You need to download Erlang to run this program.